            <figure class="media-figure img-inset-thumb"><span class="img "><img src="https://cbsnews3.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2017/09/28/a99dd172-ef3b-4553-a597-b5ef85ff5936/thumbnail/60x60/f0e5ccc56809b8e0ad689da89c51657c/istock-524538466.jpg#" alt=" " height="60" width="60" class=" lazyload" data-srcset="https://cbsnews3.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2017/09/28/a99dd172-ef3b-4553-a597-b5ef85ff5936/thumbnail/60x60/f0e5ccc56809b8e0ad689da89c51657c/istock-524538466.jpg 1x, https://cbsnews3.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2017/09/28/a99dd172-ef3b-4553-a597-b5ef85ff5936/thumbnail/120x120/a683f385edfdd7158a0e258560dd39df/istock-524538466.jpg 2x" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI="></span>
